show.description: Ek fake wedding deal, ek real attraction, aur ek ladki jise duniya ne underestimate kiya. Alicia aur Lucius ke beech ki chemistry sirf contract tak simit nahi rehne wali. Dekhiye is twisted love story “Billionaire Playboy’s Replacement Bride”, jahan har scene mein hai heat aur heartbreak.
